<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA515_04_IH_0006_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="./../../common_practice/js/ema511_ih.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema515_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema515_04_ih_0006">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="6" class="is_star" lang="y">
          <div>
            채은이는 쿠키를 만드는 데 우유
            <div class="fraction_box_wrap">
              <span>1</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>3</span>
                <span>10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            컵과 밀가루
            <div class="fraction_box_wrap">
              <span>3</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>1</span>
                <span>15</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            컵을 사용했습니다. 채은이가 사용한 우유와 밀가루는 모두 몇 컵인지 식을 쓰고 답을 구해 보세요.
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center gap_40">
          <div class="img_box">
            <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA515_04_IH/0006_img.png" alt="" />
          </div>
          <div class="div flex dir_col gap-80">
            <div class="flex align_end gap_10">
              <span class="label_gray" lang="y">식</span>
              <div class="input_wrap_underline align_center">
                <div class="mixed_fraction">
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field></div>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="10"></math-field></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                +
                <div class="mixed_fraction">
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="3" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field></div>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="15"></math-field></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                =
                <div class="mixed_fraction">
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="4" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="11"></math-field></div>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="30"></math-field></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex align_end gap_10">
              <span class="label_gray" lang="y">답</span>
              <div class="input_wrap_underline align_end">
                <div class="mixed_fraction">
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="4" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="11"></math-field></div>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="30"></math-field></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap answer3">
                  <math-field
                    data-answer-single="4(11)/(30)(=(131)/(30))"
                    data-answer-multi='{"values": ["4(11)/(30)", "(131)/(30)""]}'
                    text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div> -->
              </div>
              <span lang="y" class="line_height_1">컵</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">(채은이가 사용한 우유 양과 밀가루 양의 합)</p>
                <!--start solve-->
                <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
                  <span>=</span>
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span class="whole">1</span>
                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span>10</span>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <span>+</span>
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span class="whole">3</span>
                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span>15</span>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <span>=</span>
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span class="whole">1</span>
                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>9</span>
                      <span>30</span>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <span>+</span>
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span class="whole">3</span>
                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>2</span>
                      <span>30</span>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <span>=</span>
                  <div class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span class="whole">4</span>
                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>11</span>
                      <span>30</span>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <span> (컵)</span>
                </div>
                <!--end solve-->
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="buttons_solve">
                  
              </div> -->
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
